=== Additivity ===
It follows from the definition of the chi-squared distribution that the sum of independent chi-squared variables is also chi-squared distributed. Specifically, if formula_80 are independent chi-squared variables with formula_81, formula_82 degrees of freedom, respectively, then formula_83 is chi-squared distributed with formula_84 degrees of freedom.

