* &quot;Band of Brothers&quot;, a 2001 miniseries about 101st Airborne Division in WW2.
* &quot;I Am an American Soldier&quot;, a 2007 documentary movie that followed C co, 3 BCT during its tour of duty in Iraq in 2006.
* &quot;Battleground&quot;, a 1949 American war film that follows a company in the 327th Glider Infantry Regiment, as they fight in the siege of Bastogne during the Battle of the Bulge.

