<doc id="113481" wikidata="Q2091863" url="?curid=113481" title="Pianissimo (disambiguation)">
<text>[[Pianissimo]] is a term in music dynamics meaning &quot;to be played very softly.&quot;

Pianissimo may also refer to:

*&quot;Pianissimo&quot;, a 1990 album by Suzanne Ciani
* &quot;Pianissimo&quot;, a part of the &quot;Requiem&quot; trilogy by Virgin Black

